name: elders Labyrinth Free
description:
WARNING: For maximum effect please use headphones with high volume!

Welcome to Elder's Labyrinth, a terrifying experience in the depths of darkness. Do you have the Skills to escape?...
There are 4 keys hidden in the labyrinth that open the gate to the exit but remember to keep on the move and watch your back, your not alone.




Music:
